title: World ranking of Faroe Islands ' national football team 1993 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing FIFA World Ranking position, containing a total of 27 data points.
Overall FIFA World Ranking position has decreased over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2008 and 2009.
The highest FIFA World Ranking position, of value 194.0 was reached at Year 2007
The lowest FIFA World Ranking position, of value 83.0 was reported at Year 2016
